"The user starts with View 1 (Overview) to examine the overall relationship between Churn Score and CLTV. After selecting high-risk clusters using brush selection, View 2 (Exploration) reveals retention patterns through tenure-referral heatmap analysis. Simultaneously, View 3 (Exploration) shows how service bundles correlate with churn reasons for the selected population. Interactions in View 2 further refine service bundle analysis in View 3."